usiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1913.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Help with weapon selection and dual wielding</span><hr size=1> Starting at level 28, the primary hand gets a damage bonus.<br>
<br>
For 1 handed weapons (fists included) this bonus is calculated as (level-25)/3 rounded down.  This means that to get best damage, before level 28 the ratio of damage to delay is all that matters.<br>
<br>
What level is your monk now? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udaleb123.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daleb123</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 316<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/30/02 4:45:09 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1913.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Damage Bonus</span><hr size=1> The key to understanding the Damage Bonus is to understand that it ADDS to each hit with the primary hand. This means that getting it more frequently means more damage over a period of time.<br>
<br>
For 2-handed weapons, the Damage Bonus varies with the Delay of the weapon as well as the Level of the wielder - so that slower weapons receive larger bonuses. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=1913.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showNextMessage?topicID=1913.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1913.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.emailToFriend?topicID=1913.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.threadControl?topicID=1913.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1913.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1913.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="monklybusiness43508frm13">Board Rules<option value="monklybusiness43508frm17">Monk Change<option value